      <h1 class="heading">WHAT IS LYD STATS?</h1>
      <p class="paragraph">LYD Stats is the provider of a currency API for the Libyan Dinar. The API provides prices for the Libyan Dinar against 6 base currencies. These currencies are the United States Dollar, EUR,  GBP, TND, TRY and the CNY. <br><br>The prices provided by the API are available on a daily basis, they are sourced directly from the prices published by the Libyan Central Bank on their website and as soon as they are available. <br><br>The API allows the user to specify the base currency they want to enquire about a price for, and the date of the price required. The API also allows the user to simply enter &quot;Today&quot; as a parameter instead of a date to obtain the price of the LYD against another currency on that day. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="div-block-2">
      <div data-w-id="14b43cea-2fe6-c370-1f53-f967e907e3f6" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="/documents/brackV6.json" data-loop="0" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="0" data-is-ix2-target="1" data-renderer="svg" data-default-duration="1.6" data-duration="0"></div>
